window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Jack Sparks died while writing this book. </p> <p>It was no secret that journalist Jack Sparks had been researching the occult for his new book. No stranger to controversy, he'd already triggered a furious Twitter storm by mocking an exorcism he witnessed. </p> <p>Then there was <i>that</i> video: 40 seconds of chilling footage that Jack repeatedly claimed was not of his making, yet it was posted from his own YouTube account. </p> <p>Nobody knew what happened to Jack in the days that followed - until now. </p>"; 
